Mama, **product content chara** ekhono main baki kaj gula holo website-er **system, SEO, WooCommerce flow, client portal, QA, security, marketing setup**. Product content just ekta layer. Full professional service website korte aro kichu important layer baki ase.

## 1. WooCommerce product setup/config baki

Product content ready holeo WooCommerce backend-e ei gula setup korte hobe:

- Product category create/confirm:
  - `one-time-orm-packages`
  - `platform-checks`
  - `orm-add-ons`
  - `small-reputation-services`

- Product price set kora
- Product image add kora
- Product short description / long description fill kora
- Custom meta fields fill kora
- Featured/recommended product mark kora jodi dorkar hoy
- Virtual product enable kora
- Product page card/product details test kora

## 2. Pricing page dynamic product display test baki

Pricing page already strategy decide kora, but final test baki:

- Product card properly category wise show hocche kina
- 9+ product hole layout break hocche kina
- Product image/price/meta properly asche kina
- View Details button product page-e jacche kina
- Order Now direct checkout/cart flow kaj korche kina
- Mobile/tablet/desktop spacing premium lagche kina

## 3. SEO Cluster Meta fill-up baki

Eta product content-er cheye alada. SEO fields `inc/seo-cluster-meta.php` system-e fill korte hobe.

Baki:

- Services page SEO cluster
- Pricing page SEO cluster
- Each product page SEO cluster
- FAQ content
- Related internal links
- Schema safe output
- No hidden keyword stuffing
- No spammy doorway page style

Example pages:

```txt
Services Page
Pricing Page
Reputation Audit Package
Review Response Setup Package
Negative Review Case Review Package
Google Business Profile Reputation Check
Trustpilot Profile Check
Yelp Review Monitoring Check
```

## 4. Checkout final QA baki

Checkout mostly default rakha hobe, but test korte hobe:

- Cart → Checkout kaj korche kina
- Billing fields validation
- Payment method kaj korche kina
- Coupon/login toggle thakle kaj korche kina
- Place order korle Thank You page-e jacche kina
- Checkout mobile spacing thik kina
- Kono custom CSS WooCommerce fields break kortese kina

## 5. Thank You page / order received test baki

Thank You page code thakleo final test baki:

- Payment success hole correct page dekhay kina
- Order summary thik ache kina
- Client portal CTA kaj korche kina
- Ordered service list thik ache kina
- WooCommerce hook output thik ache kina

